author: Topsy
description:
Last weekend, the Ultramarines were graced with a selection of new models, and they will continue to play a key role in the 500 Worlds campaign going forward. Today, we present to you our top 5 Ultramarines posts. Everything is included, from inspiring miniature showcases to tutorials and reviews, because Ultramarines have always been extremely popular within the Tale of Painters crew.

The post Top 5: Ultramarines posts appeared first on Tale of Painters.
title: Top 5: Ultramarines posts
